Peer-to-Peer Video chat using webRTC

What it'll do
  Get video from your webcam
  Stream video between two computers (browsers).

What you'll need
  You must have Node.js Installed. (https://nodejs.org)
  Basic knowledge of HTML, CSS and JavaScript, Node.JS.
  Knowledge of webRTC (https://webrtc.org)

How to run
  Open terminal and go to main directory of project
  Run 'npm install' in cmd
  Start server by command 'node index.js'
  Open 'localhost:8080' in your browser and from other computer.
  
  To run from other computer, use your IP address instead of localhost
  eg, 192.168.10.4:8080
  Replace '192.168.10.4' with your IP address.

